location.fullValue: The Salerno Model Plan, Village Pointe, Suffolk VA - A Napolitano Homes Built Commun

data.description: Country living ranch style home on 11.71 acres. Featuring large spacious rooms, LVP & trim molding throughout. This  home is perfect if you like to entertain. Kitchen boasts black appliances, plenty of cabinets for storage, countertops, and two  islands wonderful for entertaining. Master BR has double sinks, vanity cabinet, and a large soaking garden tub, includes a  walk-in-closet. Rooms in the back can be used as a theatre room and lounge great for family movie nights. Great outdoor  space that is zoned for horses. This home has convenient access to shopping, downtown Suffolk and surrounding Hampton Roads cities.  First year home warranty provided by the seller.
